title: Call bank on Monday
text: Call the bank and open new account.

title: Update website
text: Update website with new products and prices.

title: Check in with clients
text: Call new clients. Check in with existing clients. Let them know about new products.

title: Reschedule delivery
text: Call UPS and reschedule Friday's delivery to Tuesday, due to holiday.

title: Pay 2QTR taxes
text: Meet with accountant to finalize taxes for 2nd quarter

title: Finish payroll
text: Finish payroll by Wednesday night and submit.
